Source: https://github.com/No-Instructions/Relay/tree/main/src/y-codemirror.next
Relay forked Kevin Jahns's y-codemirror.next (LICENSE.upstream) so that ytext
and awareness lookup could be dynamic per-EditorView (resolved every update
cycle via Obsidian's editorInfoField), which is the structural fix for the
"facet caching" bug yjs/y-codemirror.next#19 across Obsidian's view-recycling
file switches.

The TypeScript files in this directory (y-sync.ts, y-remote-selections.ts,
y-collab.ts) are a clean reimplementation of Relay's approach against
obsidian-collab's own session / context types — not a verbatim copy. Relay's
license is reproduced here because the design pattern (and a couple of
specific defensive checks) are derived from their work.
